  "name": "RPlog_Convincing_Sel_To_Talk_To_Her_Mother",
  "title": "Convincing Sel to Talk to Her Mother",
  "summary": "Aboard ship, the crimson Twi'lek engineer Ka'una, the quiet Sarian Lila, and the Falleen-tempered Serenella cross paths in a turbolift and gather in Captain Bruno's ready room over a bottle of his hidden whiskey. Lila gently steers the conversation toward family, drawing out both Ka'una's painful break from her parents on Ryloth and Serenella's estrangement from her mother on Vorzyd V. Using a cargo pickup on Vorzyd V as a pretext, Lila and Ka'una coax a reluctant Serenella into making the trip to see her mother, dangling the chance to learn the identity of her father and to give her daughter Tara grandparents. Serenella eventually relents and agrees to fly Ka'una out with Tara in tow. Ka'una then sweet-talks Captain Bruno into approving the leave, and the plan is settled.",
